Package: scReportDE
Type: Package
Title: Single-Cell Differential Expression Interactive HTML Report
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Kee-gong Karios",
                  family = "Park",
                  email = "karioslion0517@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generate self-contained interactive HTML reports from single-cell
    RNA-seq differential expression results. Accepts Seurat objects and runs
    FindMarkers/FindAllMarkers internally, or consumes pre-computed DE data.frames.
    Produces a styled report with volcano plots, interactive DE tables, dot plots,
    and violin plots. Part of the scReport ecosystem alongside scReportLite and
    scReportComposition.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    plotly,
    htmltools,
    jsonlite,
    DT
Suggests:
    Seurat,
    SeuratObject
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
